---
title: Sweet Thai Chili Pork Filet with Zesty Rice & Roasted Green Beans
description: The pan sauce on tonight’s pork is sweeeet (and spicy). Our chefs combined sweet Thai chili sauce with ponzu, shallot, lime, and butter—a winning combination with pork filet. You’ll prep fluffy zesty rice and tender roasted green beans on the side. If this sounds like a meal fit for a restaurant-worthy night, that’s ‘cause it is (just in your PJs in the comfort of your own home!).
